note:
During the course of Pyro Equity’s evolution, Iommi & Rath bought two transportation companies & merged them to create what is known as fetii. An on-demand group transportation & ride-sharing service complete with a user-friendly app, Fetii has been called “uber of group transportation.” When Iommi & Rath spotted demand that Uber and Lyft were unable to satisfy, they crafted the new company to serve an untapped market. Fetii vehicles can transport up to 30 people.
http://pyroequity.com/fetii-app
